PSEUDO_1: calculator_app

Pseudocode
START
  Declare variable x
  Declare variable y
  Declare variable z
  Declare variable operand 
  input x
  input operand 
  input y
  if operand == "+": 
    calculate x+y = z
    print z
  else if operand == "-":
    calculate x-y = z
    print z
else if operand == "*"
    calculate x*y = z
    print z
else if operand == "/"
    calculate x/y = z
    print z
else 
    print "undefined"
END